<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.7">
<l>vāynal lārnalla maṟaiyōti mantirattāṟ</l>
<l>pācilai nāṇaṟ paṭuttup paritivaittuk</l>
<l>kāyciṉa mākaḷi ṟaṉṉāṉeṉ kaippaṟṟit</l>
<l>tīvalañ ceyyak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that He who resembles a big male elephant with burning wrath</l>
<l>held my hand and circumambulated the [sacrificial] fire</l>
<l>as the people with a great utterance recited the good Vedas,</l>
<l>spread out the green-leaved nāṇal-grass [around the sacrificial fire uttering] mantras,</l>
<l rend="indent">and placed the kaus -grass [with that].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
